snippet.title: YOLKED Early Access Trailer (PC) Out Now
snippet.description:
YOLKED is out NOW on Steam! bit.ly/YOLKEDSteam

Follow the EGG-scruciating escape of an egg with arms!
Avoid enemies and overcome obstacles!
Collect all the costumes!
Watch out for the attic . . . Most importantly, don't crack!

Play today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1464010/Yolked/
https://hardboiledstudios.com
